HEADWORD: algorithmic
<hw>algorithmic</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>of or pertaining
to an algorithm.</def> <stype>recursive</stype>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>definitively solvable by a finite number of steps;
-- said of mathematical or logical problems. Contrasted with
<contr>heuristic</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

